title: Number_i LIVE TOUR 2024 No.I SPECIAL EDITION
overview: In January 2024, Number_i released their debut digital single GOAT. It was quickly followed by their mini album No.O -ring- in May, and their full album No.I in September of the same year. This special edition captures Number_i's live tour in Saitama Super Arena, which opened on Christmas Eve, 2024, and is the final show of their debut year.
